column2: select top # eid,Ever_had_eye_surgery_#,c.meaning AS &&&  from dbo.Eye_surgery_complications a       cross apply openjson(Ever_had_eye_surgery_#) j join metadata.columninfo m on m.column_name=&&& join metadata.encoding c on c.value=j.value AND     m.encoding_id=c.encoding_id  where j.value in (#,#)
